[Posting delayed pending further information, which has not, however,
been forthcoming - Mod.JW

This morning [Wed 9 Dec 1998 I called the Ministry of Health of
Kazakhstan. Even the Ministry is not aware of a single case of plague
in Kazakhstan, although they are making plans to make an official
announcement shortly.
--
Michael O. Favorov
