[This is all very strange. The Kazakh government is going to make an
official announcement that they do not have plague? Then what is the
cause of the big outreak that Xinhua reported? Of course, in the
former Soviet Union, anthrax was called "Siberian plague." We
anxiously await further clarification - Mod.JW
